### 2. Claude Agent Team Architecture (for Tool Building)
- **Agent Roles and Responsibilities**: Define each specialized agent (e.g., Requirements Agent, Architecture Agent, Code Generation Agent, Testing Agent, Integration Agent, Documentation Agent)
