- Validation approaches built into the tool
- Testing types and coverage (unit, integration, reconciliation)
- Acceptance criteria
- Data validation mechanisms

### 9. Risk Management
- Key risks and mitigation strategies
- Rollback procedures built into the tool
- Contingency planning
- Error handling and recovery

### 10. Governance and Organization
- Team structure for using the tool (not building it)
- Communication plan
- Change management approach
- Training requirements

### 11. Implementation Roadmap
- **Phase A: Agent Team Tool Building**
  - Milestones for tool construction
  - Timeline estimates for building
  - Success criteria for the tool
